OL,3,CArmed Forces more relevant than ever,
OL,4,Csays Plymouth defence boss
OL,6,FThe role of the Armed Forces is
OL,7,Fgrowing 'ever more relevant' in times
OL,8,Fof global conflict and uncertainty,
OL,9,Faccording to the boss of one of the
OL,10,FUK's largest defence firms.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV West Country at the
OL,13,Flaunch event for Plymouth's Armed
OL,14,FForces day, Babcock Devonport's
OL,15,Fmanaging director John Gane said the
OL,16,Fcity's military need to be ready for
OL,17,Faction at all times.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
