OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773936670
OL,3,CArmed Forces more relevant than ever,
OL,4,Csays Plymouth defence boss
OL,6,F"With the world how it is today, the
OL,7,FArmed Forces are having to play an
OL,8,Fincreasing role in world events," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"Anything we can do to support that,
OL,12,Fand celebrate the purpose they have,
OL,13,Fis fantastic.
OL,15,F"Plymouth has been supporting the
OL,16,FArmed Forces for many decades. That
OL,17,Fassociation is really strong right
OL,18,Fthroughout the city."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
