OL,3,CArmed Forces more relevant than ever,
OL,4,Csays Plymouth defence boss
OL,6,FThe UK's role in the US and Israel's
OL,7,Fwar with Iran has come under scrutiny
OL,8,Fsince the conflict began in February.
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer has chaired an
OL,11,Femergency Cobra meeting in response to
OL,12,FUK gas prices soaring to a three-year
OL,13,Fhigh.
OL,15,FJerry Josee, an Army veteran who
OL,16,Fserved in Singapore and Germany with
OL,17,F95 Commando, also attended Thursday's
OL,18,Fevent in Plymouth, to mark 100 days
OL,19,Funtil Armed Forces Day in June.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
