OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1773936670
OL,3,CArmed Forces more relevant than ever,
OL,4,Csays Plymouth defence boss
OL,6,FHe said: "You've got Ukraine, you've
OL,7,Fgot Russia, you've now got Iran and
OL,8,FAmerica. It's a little bit away from
OL,9,Fus, but it's something that could
OL,10,Finvolve us very, very quickly.
OL,12,F"So it's very important that the Armed
OL,13,FForces stay on the ball, stay well
OL,14,Ftrained and stay in contact with
OL,15,Fwhat's going on."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
